# Micro Holdings — BTC-Black Ecosystem

**Micro Holdings** is building a family of Bitcoin-inspired algorithmic tokens on Ethereum-compatible chains. All tokens are connected to the **Grokchain Oracle** for real-time Bitcoin price feeds and intelligent algorithmic execution.

## Token Family

### Core Tokens
- **BTC-Black (BTC-B)** – Flagship algorithmic coin combining Bitcoin scarcity with dynamic smart contract mechanisms.
- **BTC-Pro** – Bridge coin for liquidity and cross-ecosystem value transfer.
- **Rakz Token** – ERC-20 optimized for buying into the BTC-Black ecosystem.
- **Stakz Token** – ERC-20 optimized for selling, exiting, and staking rewards.

### Premium Tier Tokens
- **BTC-Pearl (BTC-PRL)** – Elegant, lower-volatility algorithmic token focused on stability and refined value.
- **BTC-Platinum (BTC-PLT)** – Premium high-tier token offering enhanced rewards and advanced algorithmic features.

## Project Overview
This repository contains the standalone implementation of the entire BTC-Black ecosystem, including all token contracts, buy/sell infrastructure, and oracle integration.

All tokens use custom algorithmic logic powered by real market data from the Grokchain Oracle.

